---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Group Benefits & Savings Plans | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Employer-sponsored group benefits that attract and retain great employees. Health, dental, life, disability, and group savings plans for Ontario businesses."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Group Benefits and Savings</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>If you value your employees and want to make sure they'll stick with you for the long haul, it's important to offer them an attractive set of group benefits that will keep them motivated and happy. At Heidi Blondin Financial, we help employers in Eastern Ontario build Employee Benefits and Retirement Savings programs to suit the needs of your group. We take a proactive approach to educate and build creative incentives that motivate employees to live healthier, and plan for their future.</p>
        <p>Regardless of your budget or the size of your company, we'll be happy to walk you through your options and help you select the right group benefits for your employees.</p>
        <p>Already have a plan? Let our team of experts review what you already have in place to see if your company can save money and/or maximize benefits that have more value to you and your employees.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/financial-services/group-savings-plans" class="font-sans text-brand-plum font-semibold underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-brand-plum/75 transition-colors">Group Savings Plans</a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Excellent Customer Service</h2>
        <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
          <p>At Heidi Blondin Financial, we understand that the process of choosing an Employee Benefit and Retirement Savings package can be time-consuming and complex. That's why we make it our business to offer excellent customer service every step of the way. When you work with us, we'll take the time to discuss your options and help you make the right decision for your company. Whether you're looking to offer your employees health insurance, life insurance, retirement savings, profit sharing or pension plans, we're here to provide the information you need.</p>
          <p>Give your employees a set of benefits they'll be sure to appreciate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Schedule An Appointment With Heidi Today" sub="Contact Heidi to schedule an appointment and learn how we can help you improve productivity and enhance employee satisfaction." cta="Schedule An Appointment With Heidi Today" />

</BaseLayout>
